      "author": "jkRaccoon",
      "description": "Layout/CSS fix release.\n\n## Fixed\n- **\\`box-sizing: border-box\\` on plugin elements.** A button or card with \\`w: \\\"100%\\\"\\` was overflowing its parent because the default \\`box-sizing: content-box\\` adds padding/border on top of the declared width. Scoped border-box to \\`.uis-frame\\` and descendants so widths behave predictably. Forms with full-width buttons in mobile viewports no longer bleed past the frame.\n\n## Install\n**BRAT:** BRAT → Add Beta plugin → \\`jkRaccoon/obsidian-ui-sketch\\`\n**Manual:** copy \\`main.js\\`, \\`manifest.json\\`, \\`styles.css\\` into \\`<vault>/.obsidian/plugins/ui-sketch/\\`",
