      "author": "jkRaccoon",
      "description": "Bug fix release.\n\n## Fixed\n- **col with flex:0 no longer collapses to 0 width** ([#commits](../../commits/0.2.2)). Fixed-width sidebars (\\`col{flex:0}\\` with a \\`sidebar{w:220}\\` child) were rendering the sidebar items bleeding out of the flex container. Now uses \\`flex: 0 0 auto\\` so the col sizes to its content, while \\`flex > 0\\` keeps classic grow/shrink behavior.\n\n## Meta\n- Added GitHub Actions CI (\\`typecheck\\` + \\`test\\` + \\`build\\`, component-docs drift check, screenshot list drift check)\n- gen-component-docs script now emits Korean tables for \\`docs/ko/\\` automatically\n\n## Install\n**BRAT:** BRAT → Add Beta plugin → \\`jkRaccoon/obsidian-ui-sketch\\`\n**Manual:** copy \\`main.js\\`, \\`manifest.json\\`, \\`styles.css\\` into \\`<vault>/.obsidian/plugins/ui-sketch/\\`",
