      "author": "jkRaccoon",
      "description": "Community plugin readiness patch. No user-visible feature changes.\n\n## Changes\n- **Removed `innerHTML` from `renderEmptyPlaceholder`** in favor of DOM API, per Obsidian plugin guidelines.\n- **Added justification comment** for the remaining sanitized `innerHTML` call in the ` raw: ` component — input is always piped through ` sanitize-html ` with a strict allow-list.\n- **Added ` fundingUrl `** to ` manifest.json ` (GitHub Sponsors).\n- **Added ` versions.json `** for per-version ` minAppVersion ` mapping.\n\n## Install\n\n**BRAT (recommended during beta):** BRAT → Add Beta plugin → ` jkRaccoon/obsidian-ui-sketch `\n\n**Manual:** copy ` main.js `, ` manifest.json `, ` styles.css ` into ` <vault>/.obsidian/plugins/ui-sketch/ `.",
