      "author": "jkRaccoon",
      "description": "First public beta release.\n\n## Highlights\n- **44 components** across 8 categories (layout, navigation, basic input, advanced input, display, feedback, data, placeholder) + ` raw: ` HTML escape hatch\n- **L3 inline errors** with Levenshtein-based typo suggestions — the rest of the wireframe still renders\n- **Per-component zod schemas** for strict prop validation\n- **Safety caps**: max depth 32, max nodes 5000 per block; ` raw: ` piped through ` sanitize-html `\n- **Two layout models**: flex (row/col nesting) and named-area grid\n- **Viewport presets**: desktop / tablet / mobile / custom\n- **Theme adaptive**: inherits Obsidian CSS variables\n\n## Install\n\n**BRAT (recommended for beta):**\n1. Install the BRAT community plugin\n2. BRAT → Add Beta plugin → ` jkRaccoon/obsidian-ui-sketch `\n\n**Manual:** copy ` main.js `, ` manifest.json `, ` styles.css ` into ` <vault>/.obsidian/plugins/ui-sketch/ ` and enable in Settings.\n\n## Docs\n- [README (English)](https://github.com/jkRaccoon/obsidian-ui-sketch#readme)\n- [README (한국어)](https://github.com/jkRaccoon/obsidian-ui-sketch/blob/main/README.ko.md)",
